                <h3>Charge</h3>
                <p>Some abilities may have their per-life or per-refresh uses restored after they are consumed. These abilities are denoted with the word “Charge” and a number after them. In order to gain an additional per-life or per-refresh use of a Chargeable ability the Charge Incantation must be repeated in full the number of times indicated by number after Charge. For instance an ability labeled ‘Charge x3' requires three full repetitions of the Charge Incantation in order to regain a use.</p>
                <p>Unless otherwise noted:</p>
