                    <li>50': Target must be within 50' at upon completion of the incantation.</li>
                </ul>
                <p>Magic or Abilities that require physical contact may only be used provided at least one of the following is true:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>The target is willing</li>
                    <li>The target is Dead</li>
                    <li>The target is Stunned</li>
                    <li>The target is Frozen</li>
                    <li>The target is Insubstantial and unable to move from their current location.</li>
